{"timeUnixNano":"1777187806880198000","name":"gen_ai.system.message","attributes":[{"key":"content","value":{"stringValue":"[{\"text\": \"You are a helpful and professional customer support assistant for an e-commerce company.\\n\\nYour role is to:\\n- Provide accurate information using the tools available to you\\n- Be friendly, patient, and understanding with customers\\n- Always offer additional help after answering questions\\n\\nYou have access to:\\n1. get_return_policy() - Look up return policies by product category\\n2. get_product_info() - Search product information by name, ID, or keyword\\n\\nAlways use the appropriate tool rather than guessing.\"}]"}}]},{"timeUnixNano":"1777187806880211000","name":"gen_ai.user.message","attributes":[{"key":"content","value":{"stringValue":"[{\"text\": \"what products do you have\"}]"}}]},{"timeUnixNano":"1777187806880227000","name":"gen_ai.assistant.message","attributes":[{"key":"content","value":{"stringValue":"[{\"text\": \"I'd be happy to help you explore our products! However, I don't have a general catalog browsing function. \\n\\nI can search for specific products if you tell me:\\n- **A product name** (e.g., \\\"wireless headphones\\\", \\\"laptop\\\")\\n- **A product ID** (e.g., \\\"PROD-001\\\")\\n- **A keyword** (e.g., \\\"gaming\\\", \\\"bluetooth\\\", \\\"charger\\\")\\n\\nWhat type of product are you interested in? Just let me know what you're looking for, and I'll search for it for you!\"}]"}}]},{"timeUnixNano":"1777187806880239000","name":"gen_ai.user.message","attributes":[{"key":"content","value":{"stringValue":"[{\"text\": \"what tools do you have\"}]"}}]},{"timeUnixNano":"1777187810695693000","name":"gen_ai.choice","attributes":[{"key":"finish_reason","value":{"stringValue":"end_turn"}},{"key":"message","value":{"stringValue":"[{\"text\": \"I have access to two helpful tools to assist you:\\n\\n1. **get_product_info()** - This allows me to search for product information\\n   - I can search by product name (e.g., \\\"wireless headphones\\\")\\n   - Product ID (e.g., \\\"PROD-001\\\")\\n   - Or keywords (e.g., \\\"bluetooth\\\", \\\"gaming\\\")\\n   - Returns details like product name, price, category, and description\\n\\n2. **get_return_policy()** - This lets me look up return policy information\\n   - I can check return policies for specific product categories\\n   - Examples: \\\"electronics\\\", \\\"accessories\\\", \\\"audio\\\"\\n   - Returns timeframes and conditions for returns\\n\\nSo I can help you find specific products and provide information about our return policies. What would you like to know more about?\"}]"}}]}],"status":{"code":"STATUS_CODE_OK"},"flags":256},{"traceId":"P9Qar/JqumK1Wf5wKXdnKg==","spanId":"pzFvK/W4xvo=","parentSpanId":"wGpteDNTxXw=","name":"execute_event_loop_cycle","kind":"SPAN_KIND_INTERNAL","startTimeUnixNano":"1777187806880017000","endTimeUnixNano":"1777187810695757000","attributes":[{"key":"gen_ai.event.start_time","value":{"stringValue":"2026-04-26T07:16:46.880019+00:00"}},{"key":"gen_ai.operation.name","value":{"stringValue":"execute_event_loop_cycle"}},{"key":"gen_ai.system","value":{"stringValue":"strands-agents"}},{"key":"event_loop.cycle_id","value":{"stringValue":"e78aef4a-f36b-417a-9d9b-5865fb8ae955"}},{"key":"gen_ai.event.end_time","value":{"stringValue":"2026-04-26T07:16:50.695753+00:00"}}],"events":[{"timeUnixNano":"1777187806880057000","name":"gen_ai.user.message","attributes":[{"key":"content","value":{"stringValue":"[{\"text\": \"what products do you have\"}]"}}]},{"timeUnixNano":"1777187806880080000","name":"gen_ai.assistant.message","attributes":[{"key":"content","value":{"stringValue":"[{\"text\": \"I'd be happy to help you explore our products! However, I don't have a general catalog browsing function. \\n\\nI can search for specific products if you tell me:\\n- **A product name** (e.g., \\\"wireless headphones\\\", \\\"laptop\\\")\\n- **A product ID** (e.g., \\\"PROD-001\\\")\\n- **A keyword** (e.g., \\\"g